{
  "texts": [
    "GPT-OSS-20B is an opensource, decoder-only Transformer model with approximately 24 billion parameters.",
    "It is pretrained using autoregressive language modeling on a large-scale multilingual and domaindiverse corpus.",
    "The model is publicly available via the Hugging Face platform and supports efficient adaptation techniques.",
    "This choice allows us to evaluate LLM performance on structured numeric in power systems under realistic resource constraints.",
    "All experiments are conducted on a workstation equipped with two NVIDIA RTX 6000 Ada GPUs, each with 48 GB of memory."
  ]
}